iv><div style=\"text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">这段量身定制的教育之旅由我们英国霍利斯经验丰富的老师精心设计并指导，并将为学生带来无与伦比的学习体验。我们精心打造的课程不仅能全面提升学生的英语水平，让他们沉浸于听、读、说、写的学习中，还能激发他们的好奇心，培养他们在各个学科领域的热情。从科学、技术、工程和数学（STEM）领域的创新探索、编程技能的掌握，到艺术创作的表达，再到游泳运动方面的卓越表现，每一门课程都能让学生在充满活力、学术氛围浓厚的环境中激发自身的成长、创造力和学习的乐趣。</p></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p></div><div style=\"margin: 10px 0%;text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: 50%;padding: 0px 5px 0px 0px;align-self: center;flex: 0 0 auto;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img alt=\"即将截止！加入夏令营报名末班车 Last Call to Register for LEHF Summer Camp\" src=\"//www.ieduchina.com/uploadfile/202507/f18220250728083242.jpg\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\"></div></div></div><div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: 50%;padding: 0px 0px 0px 5px;align-self: center;flex: 0 0 auto;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 0%;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img alt=\"即将截止！加入夏令营报名末班车 Last Call to Register for LEHF Summer Camp\" src=\"//www.ieduchina.com/uploadfile/202507/f35120250728083244.jpg\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\"></div></div></div></div><div style=\"margin: 10px 0%;text-align: left;justify-