line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img alt=\"即将截止！加入夏令营报名末班车 Last Call to Register for LEHF Summer Camp\" src=\"//www.ieduchina.com/uploadfile/202507/f21120250728083254.jpg\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\"></div></div><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img alt=\"即将截止！加入夏令营报名末班车 Last Call to Register for LEHF Summer Camp\" src=\"//www.ieduchina.com/uploadfile/202507/f22420250728083254.jpg\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\"></div></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">在英国霍利斯的老师们的热情引领下，我们的暑期夏令营项目将乐趣与探索巧妙融合——既激发求知的火花，又悉心培养自信与创造力，助力学生收获终身友谊。而这，仅仅是精彩的开端！</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">更多精心设计的惊喜即将揭晓，我们会让每一刻都充满充实感、启发性与非凡体验，敬请持续关注！</p></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p></div><div style=\"justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;align-self: center;flex: 0 0 auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;background-color: rgb(197, 21, 52);padding: 5px 20px;margin: 0px;border-radius: 50px;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;font-size: 17px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">收费标准及报名</strong></p></div></div><div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;align-self: center;flex: 0 0 auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;margin: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 28px;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img alt=\"即将截止！加入夏令营报名末班车 Last Call to Register for LEHF Summer Camp\" src=\"//www.ieduchina.com/uploadfile/202507/f53120250728083236.jpg\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\"></div></div></div><div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;align-self: center;flex: 100 100 0%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"background-color: rgb(228, 43, 42);height: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;\"></div></div></div></div><div style=\"margin: 20px 0px 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img alt=\"即将截止！加入夏令营报名末班车 Last Call to Register for LEHF Summer Camp\" src=\"//www.ieduchina.com/uploadfile/202507/f71220250728083255.jpg\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\"></div></div></div></div></div><div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: 50%;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 98%;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;box-sizing