ite-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Sign up now for an exciting&nbsp;</span></strong></em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">British summer experience!</span></strong></em></p></div><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 37%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img alt=\"即将截止！加入夏令营报名末班车 Last Call to Register for LEHF Summer Camp\" src=\"//www.ieduchina.com/uploadfile/202507/f24520250728083230.jpg\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\"></div></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">This August, the British-style summer programme at LEH Foshan will give your children an unforgettable summer of growth and discovery!&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Led by our outstanding LEH London teachers, with support from LEH Foshan’s dedicated teaching staff,</strong>&nbsp;the programme delivers immersive courses designed to enhance English fluency while sparking curiosity in STEM, arts, sports, and more, all within a dynamic and nurturing environment.</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">Our expert faculty,&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">drawn from our sister sch