verflow-wrap: break-word !important;display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;min-width: 10%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;align-self: center;box-sizing:border-box;\"><div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 18px;color: #2e3d8e;text-align: justify;\"><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">体育锻炼</span></span></strong></p></div></div></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;color: #000000;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;font-family:\" pingfang=\"\" sc\",=\"\" system-ui,=\"\" -apple-system,=\"\" blinkmacsystemfont,=\"\" \"helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" \"hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" gb\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" ui\",=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"=\"\"><br></p><div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px 30px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;color: #000000;font-size: 14px;text-align: justify;background-color: #ffffff;text-decoration-thickness: initial;line-height: 2.5;letter-spacing: 2px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">每天坚持锻炼1-2小时，增强体质。</span></span></p></div></div>', '2025-07-28 08:38:00', 'education', 5593, 'https://www.ieduchina.com/uploadfile/202507/f51620250728083806.jpg', '上海', 'shanghai', 2025, 7);
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES (130720, '深圳普高录取率不足50%？想转轨DSE还来得及吗？', '<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img alt=\"深圳普高录取率不足50%？想转轨DSE还来得及吗？\" src=\"//www.ieduchina.com/uploadfile/202507/f56820250728084016.jpg\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\"></div></div><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px 0px 10px;width: 100%;align-self: flex-start;background-size: auto;background-repeat: repeat;background-position: 0% 0%;background-attachment: scroll;background-image: url(\" www.ieduchina.com=\"\" uploadfile=\"\" 202507=\"\" f98820250728084021.jpg\");box-sizing:=\"\" border-box;\"=\"\"><div style=\"justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;width: 100%;align-self: flex-start;padding: 19px 10px;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;font-size: 15px;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">2025年，<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">全国高考报名人数攀升至1335万</strong>，这一庞大数字中，还包含了那些选择“二战”乃至“三战”的复读生群体。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">与之形成鲜明对比的是香港DSE考试，<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 49, 142);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">2025年该考试的报考人数仅有5.5万，其中来自内地的自修生更是只有2538多人</strong></span>，两者竞争压力的差距可谓云泥之别。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">“孩子中考结束，家长们心里七上八下，纠结着究竟是让孩子去普通高中搏一搏高考，还是狠下心送孩子读<a href=\"http://schoollist.ieduchina.com/schlist/c2-p0-c0-g0-s4/\" target=\"_blank\">国际高中</a>？难道就没有别的选择了吗？”</p></div></div></div><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><div style=\"font-size: 15px;padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">最近，不少深圳家长都陷入了这样的纠结之中。而这份纠结的根源，正是深圳中考那低至50%的公办普高升学率，这升学难度简直堪称“地狱模式”！</p></div><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><div style=\"margin: 10px 0% 0px;text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;width: 100%;border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(0, 49, 142);background-color: rgb(255, 254, 251);padding: 10px;align-self: flex-start;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img alt=\"深圳普高录取率不足50%？想转轨DSE还来得及吗？\" src=\"//www.ieduchina.com/uploadfile/202507/f76320250728084017.jpg\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" width=\"100%\"></div></div></div><div style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(160, 160, 160);box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">图源：深圳市招生考试办公室</p></div><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><div style=\"margin: 10px 0% 0px;text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;width: 100%;border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(0, 49, 142);background-color: rgb(255, 254, 251);padding: 10px;align-self: flex-start;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img alt=\"深圳普高录取率不足50%？想转轨DSE还来得及吗？\" src=\"//www.ieduchina.com/uploadfile/202507/f94220250728084017.jpg\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" width=\"100%\"></div></div></div><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><div style=\"font-size: 15px;padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">近年来，深圳持续发力扩充公办高中的学位数量，然而现实却颇为严峻。在人口不断增长以及中职分流政策持续推进的双重影响下，最终仍有约半数的学生难以进入公办普通高中就读。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">2025年，深圳中考考生人数预计将攀升至14.4万，相较于2024年的13.5万，增加了近9000人。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">再看公办普高学位情况，尽管预计会从2024年的6.9万个增至7.1万个，但新增学位仅有2600个。照此情形，公办普高的录取率极有可能下滑，甚至无法达到50%这一关键比例。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">据相关统计，预估全市公办普高的招生计划约为7.2万人。按照这个数据推算：</p></div><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px 0px 10px;width: 100%;align-self: flex-start;background-size: auto;background-repeat: repeat;background-position: 0% 0%;background-attachment: scroll;background-image: url(\" www.ieduchina.com=\"\" uploadfile=\"\" 202507=\"\" f98820250728084021.jpg\");box-sizing:=\"\" border-box;\"=\"\"><div style=\"justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;padding: 19px 10px;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 49, 142);box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">今年预计会有6万多中考学生无法进入公办普高学习！</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">这也就表明，仍有将近一半的学生得另寻升学途径！</strong></p></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p></div><div style=\"line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img alt=\"深圳普高录取率不足50%？想转轨DSE还来得及吗？\" src=\"//www.ieduchina.com/uploadfile/202507/f42720250728084017.jpg\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" width=\"100%\"></div></div></div></div></div><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><div style=\"font-size: 15px;padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">50%的公办普高升学率，意味着半数学生得在职业高中和费用高昂的国际高中间做选择。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">即便考上普高，未来也要和千万人竞争，<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">内地高考一本录取率仅约15%</strong>。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">国际高中6年花费动辄百万</strong>，有预算的家庭或许有诸多选择，但对于大多数深圳的普通家长来说，这仍是一笔难以承受的巨额开支。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">内地与香港升学形势对比下，不少深圳中产家长打算送孩子去<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 49, 142);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">香港插班，转战DSE赛道</strong></span>。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">最近我们的老师常被咨询：<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">中考后转香港读高中咋操作？现在转DSE晚不晚？香港插班还有学校吗？</strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 49, 142);box-sizing: border-box;\">提醒家长，中考后想让孩子转学香港插班，别因信息差误事！</span></strong></p></div><div style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 14px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p></div><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><div style=\"text-align: center;margin: 10px 0%;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: inline-block;min-width: 10%;max-width: 100%;vertical-align: top;box-shadow: rgb(0, 49, 142) 0px 0px 4px inset;padding: 5px 15px;background-repeat: repeat;background-attachment: scroll;border-width: 4px;border-radius: 20px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(242, 245, 253);overflow: hidden;background-image: url(\" www.ieduchina.com=\"\" uploadfile=\"\" 202507=\"\" f83320250728084021.jpg\");background-position:=\"\" 0%=\"\" !important;background-size:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;box-sizing:=\"\" border-box;\"=\"\"><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 49, 142);font-size: 18px;text-align: left;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">内地孩子赴港读书条件</strong></p></div></div></div><div style=\"font-size: 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p></div><div style=\"font-size: 15px;padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">内地孩子若计划赴港读书，需先确认是否满足以下条件：</p></div><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><div style=\"margin: 10px 0%;text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;width: 100%;background-color: rgb(242, 245, 253);align-self: flex-start;padding: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\"><ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">孩子是否拥有香港身份？</strong></p></li><li><p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">孩子的学术成绩与英文水平能否达到香港学校标准？</strong></p></li><li><p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">孩子能否接受降级插班就读？</strong></p></li></ul></div></div><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><div style=\"font-size: 15px;padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">需特别强调，<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 49, 142);text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: wavy;text-decoration-color: rgb(255,202,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">拥有香港身份是内地孩子转学香港插班的必要前提！</strong></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">只有满足这一首要条件，后续事宜方可推进！</strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">若孩子尚未取得香港身份，家长需即刻着手规划，务必争分夺秒。因为香港学校在<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">中五、中六</strong>阶段，<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">基本不再接收插班生！</strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">那么，<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">内地家长如何能快速为孩子办理香港身份呢？</strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">若家长拥有本科及以上学历，即便非名校毕业、无大厂工作经历，也可通过<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">进修方式</strong>快速获取香港身份；若学历不足，但过去一年税前年收入达250万港币或以上，可尝试通过<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">香港高才计划A类</strong>为孩子快速办理香港身份。这两种方式，是目前<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">较为快捷的获取途径</strong>。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">若孩子已具备香港身份，且中考后有意转学香港插班，可按以下步骤操作！</p></div><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><div style=\"margin: 10px 0px;text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;background-color: rgb(240, 244, 255);align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"margin: 0px;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 10%;vertical-align: middle;background-color: rgb(0, 49, 142);padding: 9px;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;margin: 0px;align-self: center;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">►</p></div></div><div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;min-width: 10%;max-width: 100%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;align-self: center;margin: 0px 0px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 49, 142);text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">把握今年秋季插班最后机会</strong></p></div></div></div></div></div><div style=\"font-size: 15px;padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">孩子中考后回港插班，此时<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">年级偏高，在学位空缺和申请时间上均不占优</strong>，<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: wavy;text-decoration-color: rgb(255,202,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: wavy;text-decoration-color: rgb(255,202,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;color: rgb(0, 49, 142);box-sizing: border-box;\">精准择校定位</span></strong></span>显得尤为关键！</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">家长要尽快评估孩子的学术水平，为孩子挑选出适配且目前仍开放申请的香港学校。</strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">别再一味执着于名校或盲目海投啦！</strong>若您不知从何入手，不妨添加小助手微信，获取专业一对一咨询服务。</p></div><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><div style=\"margin: 10px 0px;text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;background-color: rgb(240, 244, 255);align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"margin: 0px;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: 10%;background-color: rgb(0, 49, 142);padding: 9px;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;margin: 0px;align-self: center;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">►</p></div></div><div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;min-width: 10%;max-width: 100%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;align-self: center;margin: 0px 0px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 49, 142);text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">提前布局明年春季香港插班</strong></p></div></div></div></div></div><div style=\"font-size: 15px;padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">要是您对学校有特定要求，或者心仪学校秋季插班报名已截止，那么当下就该着手规划明年春季插班了。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">别觉得明年春季插班时间尚早，实际上，<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">9月起就会陆续有学校开启报名通道！</strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">此时正好利用暑假黄金期，提前助力孩子查漏补缺、提升考前能力，如此一来，届时便能一举斩获名校录取通知书！</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">若您家孩子<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">正在读中学</strong>，还在<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">犹豫是否中考后赴港插班</strong>，<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 49, 142);box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: wavy;text-decoration-color: rgb(255,202,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;box-sizing: border-box;\">建议尽早规划，越早越好！</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">因为香港中四（相当于内地高一）入学时就需确定&nbsp;<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: wavy;text-decoration-color: rgb(255,202,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: wavy;text-decoration-color: rgb(255,202,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;color: rgb(0, 49, 142);box-sizing: border-box;\">DSE选科</span></strong></span>，而多数学校中三下学期便开始填写选课表。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">孩子尽早插班，一方面能选到心仪的热门科目，为未来考 DSE 升大学助力；另一方面也能有更多时间适应香港的教学方式与学习环境。</strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">若错过 DSE 选科，孩子选不到喜欢的热门科目，学习缺乏动力，进而引发一系列恶性连锁反应，最终影响大学报考。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">另一方面，<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">这两年香港插班竞争愈发激烈，肉眼可见地变难了！</strong>高年级回港插班，上千人竞争寥寥几个插班名额已成为常态，对孩子而言是不小的挑战。所以，<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">若条件允许，建议尽早赴港插班，切勿硬拖到中考后！</strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">孩子中考后想转轨香港插班，时间紧迫。作为家长，要在有限时间内获取真实可靠的香港插班信息，打破信息差，抓住每一个机会，才能将“上岸率”提升至最高！</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p></div><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><div style=\"text-align: center;margin: 10px 0%;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: inline-block;min-width: 10%;max-width: 100%;vertical-align: top;box-shadow: rgb(0, 49, 142) 0px 0px 4px inset;padding: 5px 15px;background-repeat: repeat;background-attachment: scroll;border-width: 4px;border-radius: 20px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(242, 245, 253);overflow: hidden;background-image: url(\" www.ieduchina.com=\"\" uploadfile=\"\" 202507=\"\" f83320250728084021.jpg\");background-position:=\"\" 0%=\"\" !important;background-size:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;box-sizing:=\"\" border-box;\"=\"\"><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 49, 142);font-size: 18px;text-align: left;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-align: left;box-sizing: border-box;\">中考后三条路</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">普高、国际高中、DSE的对比</strong></p></div></div></div><div style=\"font-size: 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p></div><div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px -20px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);padding: 0px 13px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"margin: 2px 0px -2px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 49, 142);padding: 0px 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">普通高中</strong></span></p></div></div></div></div><div style=\"margin: -10px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;height: 10px;width: 100%;border-radius: 36px;background-color: rgba(0, 49, 142, 0.37);box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"margin: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px 0px 10px;width: 100%;align-self: flex-start;border-style: solid;border-width: 1px;border-color: rgb(0, 49, 142);padding: 10px 3px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;padding: 10px;margin: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 254, 251);box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"margin: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">普通高中宛如一条超超超拥挤的“赛道”，对于成绩出类拔萃的学生而言，或许还算是一条颇具性价比的升学之路。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: wavy;text-decoration-color: rgb(255,202,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: wavy;text-decoration-color: rgb(255,202,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;color: rgb(0, 49, 142);box-sizing: border-box;\">优势：</span></strong></span>学费亲民，每年仅需 1 - 3 万，对于那些成绩顶尖、能很好地适应高考题海战术的学生来说，是不错的选择。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: wavy;text-decoration-color: rgb(255,202,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: wavy;text-decoration-color: rgb(255,202,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;color: rgb(0, 49, 142);box-sizing: border-box;\">劣势：</span></strong></span>竞争白热化，以 2023 年广东高考为例，考生人数超 70 万。而且，985 高校的录取率仅有 2.3%，普通高中的学生想要进入名校，难度正逐年递增！</p></div></div></div></div></div><div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-ali