, 255, 255);text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">►</p></div></div><div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;min-width: 10%;max-width: 100%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;align-self: center;margin: 0px 0px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 49, 142);text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">升学优势显著，多元选择随心</strong></p></div></div></div></div></div><div style=\"font-size: 15px;padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: wavy;text-decoration-color: rgb(255,202,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: wavy;text-decoration-color: rgb(255,202,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;color: rgb(0, 49, 142);box-sizing: border-box;\">升学路径超灵活：</span></strong></span>凭借这条路径，学生可申请香港、内地、英国、澳洲等全球 600 多所知名高校，真正实现“全球升学自由”，为未来发展铺就宽广道路。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: wavy;text-decoration-color: rgb(255,202,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: wavy;text-decoration-color: rgb(255,202,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;color: rgb(0, 49, 142);box-sizing: border-box;\">竞争压力相对小：</span></strong></span>相较于传统升学赛道，此路径的全球考生仅 5.5 万人，竞争氛围相对宽松，学生有更多机会脱颖而出。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: wavy;text-decoration-color: rgb(255,202,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: wavy;text-decoration-color: rgb(255,202,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;color: rgb(0, 49, 142);box-sizing: border-box;\">语言环境超友好：</span></strong></span>采用中英双语应试模式，既兼顾了学生对母语的熟悉与掌握，又能有效提升英语能力，为国际化学习奠定坚实基础。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: wavy;text-decoration-color: rgb(255,202,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: wavy;text-decoration-color: rgb(255,202,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;color: rgb(0, 49, 142);box-sizing: border-box;\">评估方式更科学：</span></strong></span>避免了“一考定终生”的弊端，通过多元化的评估体系，全面、客观地考量学生的综合素养与学术能力，让每个学生的闪光点都能被看见。</p></div><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><div style=\"margin: 10px 0px;text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;background-color: rgb(240, 244, 255);align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"margin: 0px;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: 10%;background-color: rgb(0, 49, 142);padding: 9px;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;margin: 0px;align-self: center;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">►</p></div></div><div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;min-width: 10%;max-width: 100%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;align-self: center;margin: 0px 0px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 49, 142);text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">名校录取优势，一目了然</strong></p></div></div></div></div></div><div style=\"font-size: 15px;padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: wavy;text-decoration-color: rgb(255,202,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: wavy;text-decoration-color: rgb(255,202,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;color: rgb(0, 49, 142);box-sizing: border-box;\">名校录取率：</span></strong></span>这条路径的优势更是十分突出。以香港八大高校为例，在 DSE 考生中，香<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">港本地生升读港八大的比例超过30%</strong>，这意味着每三个本地生中就有一个能进入顶尖学府深造。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: wavy;text-decoration-color: rgb(255,202,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: wavy;text-decoration-color: rgb(255,202,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;color: rgb(0, 49, 142);box-sizing: border-box;\">竞争人数：</span></strong></span>DSE赛道今年仅有5.5万人报考，而高考的报考人数高达1335万人，D<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">SE的竞争规模仅为高考的 0.4%</strong>。如此鲜明的对比，充分彰显了这条“第三条路”在名校升学方面的巨大优势。</p></div><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><div style=\"margin: 10px 0% 0px;text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;width: 100%;border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(0, 49, 142);background-color: rgb(255, 254, 251);padding: 10px;align-self: flex-start;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img alt=\"深圳普高录取率不足50%？想转轨DSE还来得及吗？\" src=\"//www.ieduchina.com/uploadfile/202507/f30720250728084017.jpg\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" width=\"100%\"></div></div></div><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><div style=\"text-align: center;margin: 10px 0%;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: inline-block;min-width: 10%;max-width: 100%;vertical-align: top;box-shadow: rgb(0, 49, 142) 0px 0px 4px inset;padding: 5px 15px;background-repeat: repeat;background-attachment: scroll;border-width: 4px;border-radius: 20px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(242, 245, 253);overflow: hidden;background-image: url(\" www.ieduchina.com=\"\" uploadfile=\"\" 202507=\"\" f83320250728084021.jpg\");background-position:=\"\" 0%=\"\" !important;background-size:=\"\" auto=\"\" !important;box-sizing:=\"\" border-box;\"=\"\"><div style=\"color: rgb(0, 49, 142);font-size: 18px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">DSE如何规划</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">抓住三年黄金期</strong></p></div></div></div><div style=\"font-size: 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p></div><div style=\"font-size: 15px;padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">不少家长心里都犯嘀咕：孩子中考结束后再转轨DSE课程，还来得及吗？</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: wavy;text-decoration-color: rgb(255,202,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: wavy;text-decoration-color: rgb(255,202,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;color: rgb(0, 49, 142);box-sizing: border-box;\">答案毋庸置疑：完全来得及！</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: wavy;text-decoration-color: rgb(255,202,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: wavy;text-decoration-color: rgb(255,202,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;color: rgb(0, 49, 142);box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">DSE课程和内地高中知识重合度相当高，能达到70%，特别是在数理化这些科目上，内地学生基础知识学得扎实，有着天然的优势。</p></div><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><div style=\"margin: 10px 0%;text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;background-color: rgb(242, 245, 253);align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;padding: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: wavy;text-decoration-color: rgb(255,202,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: wavy;text-decoration-color: rgb(255,202,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;color: rgb(0, 49, 142);box-sizing: border-box;\">中考后（高一至高二）转轨时间规划</span></strong></span></p></div><div style=\"font-size: 8px;text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;box-sizing: border-box;\"><ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">高一转轨：最优之选</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;box-sizing: border-box;\">高一阶段转轨DSE课程是最佳时机。此时学生有充裕的时间去适应DSE课程体系，尤其是可以在英语方面进行强化提升，为后续的学习和升学打下坚实基础。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p></li><li><p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">高二转轨：需加速冲刺</strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;box-sizing: border-box;\">高二转轨适合英语基础较好的学生，一般要求<a href=\"http://www.ieduchina.com/training/ielts/ielts/\" target=\"_blank\">雅思</a>成绩达到5.5分以上。不过，由于时间相对紧张，学生需要密集补习选修科目，加快学习节奏，以跟上课程进度。</span></p></li></ul></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;font-size: 15px;padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">只要做好合理规划，中考后转轨DSE，3年的学习时间足够学生冲刺内地或者海外名校。</strong></span></p></div></div></div><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;align-self: stretch;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"font-size: 19px;margin: 0px 0%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 1.8em;height: 1.8em;line-height: 1.8em;border-radius: 100%;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;font-size: 20px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);border: 1px solid rgb(0, 49, 142);background-color: rgb(0, 49, 142);box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Q</strong></p></div></div></div></div></div><div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: stretch;flex: 100 100 0%;height: auto;background-color: rgb(240, 244, 255);margin: 0px 0px 0px -17px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 29px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"margin: 6px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"font-size: 15px;text-align: justify;color: rgb(0, 49, 142);box-sizing: border-box