ext-decoration-style: wavy;text-decoration-color: rgb(255,202,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;color: rgb(0, 49, 142);box-sizing: border-box;\">申请香港副学士：</span></strong></span>可以选择申请香港副学士，采用“2 + 2”模式衔接本科，其升学率超过80%，为学生提供了继续深造的机会。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: wavy;text-decoration-color: rgb(255,202,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: wavy;text-decoration-color: rgb(255,202,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;color: rgb(0, 49, 142);box-sizing: border-box;\">成绩合并优势：</span></strong></span>DSE成绩永久有效，在申请港校时，可以合并两年单科最佳总分，这为学生提供了更多的尝试和提升空间。</p></div></div></div></div><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;align-self: stretch;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"font-size: 19px;margin: 0px 0%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: inline-block;border: 1px solid rgb(0, 49, 142);background-color: rgb(0, 49, 142);width: 1.8em;height: 1.8em;line-height: 1.8em;border-radius: 100%;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;font-size: 20px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Q</strong></p></div></div></div></div></div><div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;align-self: stretch;flex: 100 100 0%;height: auto;background-color: rgb(240, 244, 255);margin: 0px 0px 0px -17px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 29px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"margin: 6px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(0, 49, 142);font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">英语不太好，能读DSE课程吗？</strong></p></div></div></div></div><div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 17px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;align-self: stretch;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"font-size: 19px;margin: 0px 0%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: inline-block;border: 1px solid rgba(0, 49, 142, 0.37);background-color: rgba(0, 49, 142, 0.37);width: 1.8em;height: 1.8em;line-height: 1.8em;border-radius: 100%;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;font-size: 20px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">A</strong></p></div></div></div></div></div><div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;align-self: stretch;flex: 100 100 0%;height: auto;margin: 0px 0px 0px -17px;padding: 0px 26px 0px 29px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"margin: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(48, 48, 48);font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">当然可以！DSE计分独特，3 - 5月考试，允许<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">单科补考且成绩永久有效</strong>，<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: wavy;text-decoration-color: rgb(255,202,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: wavy;text-decoration-color: rgb(255,202,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;color: rgb(0, 49, 142);box-sizing: border-box;\">申请港校可合并两年单科最佳总分</span></strong></span>，考砸科目可次年重考，取两年最优五科成绩申本科。</p></div></div></div></div><div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 95%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img alt=\"深圳普高录取率不足50%？想转轨DSE还来得及吗？\" src=\"//www.ieduchina.com/uploadfile/202507/f60320250728084018.jpg\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" width=\"100%\"></div></div><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><div style=\"font-size: 15px;padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">虽英语有难度，但允许“偏科”，英语及格、其他科目优异仍有机会进名校。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">此外，港前五（港大、港中文、港科大、港理工、港城大）还有加权政策。当学生某个学科达到5分以上，可获得额外加权分，这对于偏科的学生来说是一个很大的优势。具体加权方法如下：</p></div><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><div style=\"margin: 10px 0%;text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;width: 100%;background-color: rgb(242, 245, 253);align-self: flex-start;padding: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 49, 142);padding: 0px 10px;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: wavy;text-decoration-color: rgb(255,202,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">[5]=5分 + 0.5加权分 = 5.5分</strong></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: wavy;text-decoration-color: rgb(255,202,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></strong></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: wavy;text-decoration-color: rgb(255,202,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">[5*]=6分 + 1加权分 = 7分</strong></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: wavy;text-decoration-color: rgb(255,202,0);text-decoration-thickness: 2px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><br>[5**]=7分 + 1.5加权分 = 8.5分</strong></span></p></div></div><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><div style=\"display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0%;text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;flex: 100 100 0%;align-self: flex-start;height: auto;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: flex;flex-flow: row;text-align: center;justify-content: center;margin: 0px 0%;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: bottom;width: auto;flex: 0 0 0%;height: auto;align-self: flex-end;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"text-align: left;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 8px;height: 8px;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;background-color: rgb(0, 49, 142);box-sizing: border-box;\"></div></div></div><div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: bottom;width: auto;flex: 0 0 0%;align-self: flex-end;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"text-align: left;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 8px;height: 8px;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;background-color: rgb(0, 49, 142);box-sizing: border-box;\"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div style=\"padding: 0px 10px;color: rgb(0, 49, 142);box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">⚠️中考结束，是否在考虑要不要转DSE赛道？！由于不如行动！扫描下方小助手二维码，解锁DSE暑期课程！</strong></p></div><div style=\"font-size: 9px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p></div><div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 35%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img alt=\"深圳普高录取率不足50%？想转轨DSE还来得及吗？\" src=\"//www.ieduchina.com/uploadfile/202507/f81520250728084017.jpg\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" width=\"100%\"></div></div><div style=\"font-size: 14px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">长按扫码添加小助手</p></div><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p></div>', '2025-07-28 08:40:00', 'zt', 10974, 'https://www.ieduchina.com/uploadfile/202507/f42720250728084017.jpg', '广东', 'shenzhen', 2025, 7);
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES (130725, '香港DSE大热！还在头铁死磕贝赛思、留美的，都是什么家庭啊？', '<div style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2;box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><div style=\"text-align: unset;font-size: 12px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 24px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;text-align: left;\"><br/></p></div><div style=\"line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2;box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><div style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2;box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><div style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 2;box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\"><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \" PingFang SC \", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.5em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" PingFang SC\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(2, 30, 170);color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;留美特朗普背刺，贝赛思家长为何仍头铁？</span></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \" PingFang SC \", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.5em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" PingFang SC\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">特朗普“大而美”法案颁布后，留美学生遭遇史无前例“背刺”。留学成本攀升、签证政策收紧、毕业就业问题全都成为问题。</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \" PingFang SC \", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.5em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" PingFang SC\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">奇怪的是，</span><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">我观察到</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 76, 65);font-weight: bold;\">美系代表国际校贝赛思在深圳、北京等一线城市的热度却不见消减</span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">。</span><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">贝赛思还在如火如荼扩建新校区中</span>                                                        ，广州琶洲校区、北京顺义校区明年落成，北、上、广、深多所头部国际校<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">仍以美国为最终留学目的地。</span></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \" PingFang SC \", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.5em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" PingFang SC\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">以贝赛思为代表的头部</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 76, 65);font-weight: bold;\">美式校家长依旧非常坚定</span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">，这看似不合逻辑之下隐藏着怎样的原因？</span></span></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"香港DSE大热！还在头铁死磕贝赛思、留美的，都是什么家庭啊？\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" src=\"//www.ieduchina.com/uploadfile/202507/f85420250728084300.jpg\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;\">北京贝赛思</span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \" PingFang SC \", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.5em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" PingFang SC\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">                                                        选校君搜罗全网，以及咨询我们的家长群体的诉求后发现，<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 76, 65);font-weight: bold;\">选择留美的“精英群体”是真的“头铁”，</span>                                                        来看看选校君归纳出来的“头铁”五类家庭——</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \" PingFang SC \", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.5em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" PingFang SC\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(2, 30, 170);color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-weight: bold;\">“</span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(2, 30, 170);color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-weight: bold;font-size: 17px;\">风浪越大鱼越贵”</span></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \" PingFang SC \", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.5em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" PingFang SC\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(2, 30, 170);color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-weight: bold;font-size: 17px;\">笃定留美派：</span></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \" PingFang SC \", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.5em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" PingFang SC\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \" PingFang SC \", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.5em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" PingFang SC\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(201, 227, 185);font-weight: bold;\">1、科技新贵 &nbsp;</span>                                                        ：<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 76, 65);\">年收入50-150w</span>                                                        、孩子能<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">达到中等211以上水平</span>                                                        的中产家庭；目标高性价比公立大学、藤校、留美就业，目标硅谷/华尔街高薪职业，利用校友网路助力职业发展。读美本能更容易找到大厂正职、也能省去美硕额外两年。2025年藤校中国毕业生起薪中位数仍然比国内985毕业生高40%（但是距2015年已经缩小了15%）。</span></p><div><img alt=\"香港DSE大热！还在头铁死磕贝赛思、留美的，都是什么家庭啊？\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" src=\"//www.ieduchina.com/uploadfile/202507/f33220250728084302.jpg\" style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px;\"/></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \" PingFang SC \", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.5em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" PingFang SC\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \" PingFang SC \", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.5em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" PingFang SC\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(201, 227, 185);font-weight: bold;\">2、跨国企业主 &nbsp;</span>                                                        ：年收入200w往上的高净值家庭，有海外尤其是美国市场扩张需求的企业或高管；或者出于产业升级需要，需要子女接班赴美学习；这类家庭的客观需求使规划<a href=\"http://www.ieduchina.com/abroad/usa/\" target=\"_blank\">美国留学</a>                                                        成为刚需。</span></p><div><img alt=\"香港DSE大热！还在头铁死磕贝赛思、留美的，都是什么家庭啊？\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" src=\"//www.ieduchina.com/uploadfile/202507/f71520250728084302.jpg\" style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px;\"/></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \" PingFang SC \", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.5em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" PingFang SC\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \" PingFang SC \", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.5em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" PingFang SC\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(201, 227, 185);font-weight: bold;\">3、学术特长生：</span>                                                        自身学术实力超群，希望去美国顶尖实验室，追求更好的科研氛围。孩子能成为STEM竞赛获奖者，计划读博。对比国内高校的结构化学习，对跨学科学习有强烈好奇心、需要自由创作空间的学生。（这不就是贝赛思的学生吗<img alt=\"香港DSE大热！还在头铁死磕贝赛思、留美的，都是什么家庭啊？\" src=\"//www.ieduchina.com/uploadfile/202507/f20320250728084303.jpg\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"display:inline-block;width:20px;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/>）</span></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"香港DSE大热！还在头铁死磕贝赛思、留美的，都是什么家庭啊？\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" src=\"//www.ieduchina.com/uploadfile/202507/f82720250728100223.jpg\" style=\"width:567px;height:330px;\"/></div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">劳伦斯伯克利实验室是美国能源部历史最悠久的国家实验室，开创了核武器和能源技术，目前由加州大学进行管理运行。到2024年，伯克利实验室的科学家及团队斩获了15个诺贝尔奖和16枚美国国家科学奖章等诸多奖项。LBNL每年所培养的理工科优秀毕业生，一直在推动着美国和全世界的科技进步。</span></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \" PingFang SC \", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.5em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" PingFang SC\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \" PingFang SC \", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.5em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" PingFang SC\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(201, 227, 185);font-weight: bold;\">4、新兴产业创业者：</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" PingFang SC\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">有新兴产业或科技类行业创业规划的家庭。美国</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" PingFang SC\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">                                                        金融发达，客观上具有新兴科创行业<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">融资优势</span>                                                        ，目前来说仍然是其他地区无法比拟的。而<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">美本的创业资源也很丰富</span>                                                        ，<a href=\"http://schoollist.ieduchina.com/school/brown/\" target=\"_blank\">布朗大学</a>                                                        允许学生自创专业，这种个性化培养在国内高校几乎不可能实现。</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \" PingFang SC \", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.5em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" PingFang SC\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(201, 227, 185);font-weight: bold;\">5、移民家庭：</span>                                                        低龄留学规划家庭，在国内国际学校提前适应文化差异后，转入顶尖寄宿美高；为了让孩子开阔眼界，移民留学同步进行，对有资金分散分配需求的高净值家庭有利好。</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" PingFang SC\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;background-color: rgb(2, 30, 170);color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-weight: bold;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \" PingFang SC \", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.5em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" PingFang SC\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;background-color: rgb(2, 30, 170);color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-weight: bold;font-size: 17px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;留美，氪金大佬和学霸仍在冲：</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \" PingFang SC \", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.5em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" PingFang SC\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">在2005年左右之前，留学一直是精英的象征，是佼佼者的选择，归国留学生是有国际视角的紧缺人才；2005年之后，随着国内经济腾飞，中产也实现了财富积累、迎来留学红利期，孩子去留学学费既不会太贵，毕业后薪资待遇和社会认可度也比较高。</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \" PingFang SC \", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.5em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" PingFang SC\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">                                                        到了2018年以后，随着留学群体的增加，导致排名较高的海外大学根本不缺生源。而一些本身能力一般、又吃到留学红利的学生群体找工作时，文凭光环已经不如以前有用了。在逆全球化抬头后，留学费用高的令人发指，已经非普通中产家庭负担得起。<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">精准留学就显得格外重要了！不同家庭群体的留学策略开始分化。</span></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \" PingFang SC \", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.5em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" PingFang SC\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 30, 170);font-weight: bold;\">还在“头铁”走留美方向的家庭，要么非富即贵，要么实力超群。</span></span><strong><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" PingFang SC\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 30, 170);font-weight: bold;\">这个群体的家长回归“鱼贵”的红利期</span></span></strong><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" PingFang SC\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(2, 30, 170);font-weight: bold;\">。</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" PingFang SC\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">所以，当90%家庭撤离时，他们却重码加仓。</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \" PingFang SC \", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: init