 \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \" PingFang SC \", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.5em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" PingFang SC\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">                                                        在学历贬值，内卷严重的当下，如果孩子不是学术很强<span style=\"color: #ff4c41;\">，</span><span style=\"color: #ff4c41;font-weight: bold;\">中产家庭掏空积蓄去留学，似乎性价比并不高。</span>                                                        而转向香港、<a href=\"http://www.ieduchina.com/abroad/singapore/\" target=\"_blank\">新加坡留学</a>                                                        ，不管从性价比还是稳定性来说，都是很好的选项。选校君归纳了“弃美”的家庭想法：</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \" PingFang SC \", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.5em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" PingFang SC\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">                                                        1.担心子女<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">安全</span>                                                        问题，且无法赴美陪读；</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \" PingFang SC \", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.5em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" PingFang SC\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">                                                        2.权衡之后，觉得留美<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">性价比</span><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">不高；</span>                                                        美本四年花费大约200w，需要工作8-10年才能追平国内985本硕的经济差距。而香港或者新加坡学费则性价比较高。</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \" PingFang SC \", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.5em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" PingFang SC\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">                                                        3.未来希望<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">回国发展</span>                                                        的，即使是美国名校在国内的认可度也不如从前。有美本学生回国后因\"过于美式\"的思维方式在外企都遭遇水土不服，反而<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">双语能力突出但保留本土思维的海归更吃香‌。</span></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \" PingFang SC \", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.5em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" PingFang SC\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">                                                        4.新加坡、香港离家比较近，家长探访也方便，<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">孩子适应也快。学历认可度也高，回报周期更短、稳。</span></span></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"香港DSE大热！还在头铁死磕贝赛思、留美的，都是什么家庭啊？\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" src=\"//www.ieduchina.com/uploadfile/202507/f15320250728084308.jpg\"/></div><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \" PingFang SC \", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.5em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" PingFang SC\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"http://schoollist.ieduchina.com/school/hku/\" target=\"_blank\">香港大学</a>                                                            （2025QS排名全球第11）、<a href=\"http://schoollist.ieduchina.com/school/nus/\" target=\"_blank\">新加坡国立大学</a>                                                            （QS8）</span></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 8px 24px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \" PingFang SC \", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: left;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.5em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" PingFang SC\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">                                                        最后补充一下<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">英国方向</span>                                                        ，英国的留学成本虽然也是逐年上涨，但整体比美本低30%左右，学制短、并且签证的灵活便利性也很高</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" Helvetica Neue\", \" PingFang SC\", \" Hiragino Sans GB\", \" Microsoft YaHei UI\", \" Microsoft YaHei \", Arial, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;text-align: left;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap:', '2025-07-29 16:14:00', 'zt', 4920, 'https://www.ieduchina.com/uploadfile/202507/f85420250728084300.jpg', '广东', 'shenzhen', 2025, 7);
