;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"margin: 0px 0%;transform: translate3d(4px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(4px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(4px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(4px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 16px;height: 16px;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);border-width: 2px;border-style: solid solid none none;border-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;flex: 100 100 0%;align-self: center;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(0, 49, 142);padding: 0px 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">向下滑动查看所有内容</p></div></div></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">香港政府发现<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">部分持受养人签证的学生未实际在港居住，却以本地生身份占用教资会资助学额，影响本地学生升学机会及公帑合理分配。</strong></p></div><div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img alt=\"突袭“考试移民”—香港本地生定义修改！新港人家庭如何应对？\" src=\"//www.ieduchina.com/uploadfile/202508/f29220250804083705.jpg\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\"></div></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p></div><div style=\"text-align: justify;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">为此，教育局参考海外经验及本地实情，修订政府资助专上课程学额申请规则。</p></div></div></div></div><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;margin: 10px 0px;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: bottom;width: auto;min-width: 10%;max-width: 100%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;padding: 0px;align-self: flex-end;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"font-size: 19px;text-align: center;margin: 0px 0px 26px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: inline-block;border: 1px solid rgb(1, 36, 154);background-color: rgb(1, 36, 154);width: 1.8em;height: 1.8em;line-height: 1.8em;border-radius: 100%;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;font-size: 22px;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">1</p></div></div></div><div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: bottom;width: auto;min-width: 10%;max-width: 100%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;align-self: flex-end;margin: 0px 0px 0px -14px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"transform: rotateZ(37deg);-webkit-transform: rotateZ(37deg);-moz-transform: rotateZ(37deg);-o-transform: rotateZ(37deg);box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"margin: 0px;transform: translate3d(-1px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-1px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-1px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-1px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 28px;height: 57px;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;border-left: 1px solid rgb(1, 36, 154);border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box;\"></div></div></div></div><div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: bottom;width: auto;min-width: 10%;max-width: 100%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;margin: 0px;align-self: flex-end;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"transform: translate3d(-18px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-18px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-18px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-18px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"font-size: 19px;color: rgb(1, 36, 154);text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">核心修订内容</strong></p></div></div><div style=\"transform: translate3d(-17px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-17px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-17px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-17px, 0px, 0px);margin: -2px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"font-size: 13px;color: rgb(1, 36, 154);box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p></div></div></div></div><div style=\"font-size: 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p></div><div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;align-self: center;flex: 0 0 auto;line-height: 0;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;overflow: hidden;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-13px, 0px, 0px);margin: -3px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;ve