ox;\">对借人才计划移民的家庭，新政策出台对子女教育规划影响重大。<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">政策实施后，香港高校学位竞争加剧，政府资助学额申请更难，学位资源更紧张，稍有不慎子女或错失机会。</strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">所以，<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 49, 142);box-sizing: border-box;\">有此移民打算的家庭要尽早规划赴港读书方案，提前了解香港教育相关情况，做好充分准备。</span></strong></p></div><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><div style=\"margin: 10px 0% 0px;text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;width: 100%;border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(0, 49, 142);background-color: rgb(255, 254, 251);padding: 10px;align-self: flex-start;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\"><img alt=\"突袭“考试移民”—香港本地生定义修改！新港人家庭如何应对？\" src=\"//www.ieduchina.com/uploadfile/202508/f91320250804083706.jpg\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\"></div></div></div><div style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 49, 142);padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p></div><p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><br></p><div style=\"margin: 10px 0px;text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;background-color: rgb(240, 244, 255);align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div style=\"margin: 0px;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;\"><div s